### INEFFECTIVE_DYNAMIC_IMPORT

```text
[INEFFECTIVE_DYNAMIC_IMPORT] Warning: b.js is dynamically imported by b.js but also statically imported by a.js, dynamic import will not move module into another chunk.

```

